description.en:
What is Astro Pepe(Astropepe)?

Astro Pepe isn't just another crypto with a cute name, it's a coin with a mission. Astro Pepe's DAPP and Staking utility are out of this world, but that's just the beginning. Astro Pepe's ultimate goal is to send a physical Pepe to the moon, complete with a wallet holding AstroPepe. That's right, AstroPepe has a dream. DAPP platform of Astro Pepe project is a community hub for meme enthusiasts and crypto investors alike. With an intuitive interface and easy-to-use features, managing your $AstroPepe has never been easier.
